@startuml
object Sysadmin
object "Admin API" as AdminAPI
object "Teacher update" as TeacherUpdate
object "Teacher storage" as TeacherStorage
object "Password hasher" as PasswordHasher
object Teachers <<database>>
object "Discord bot configuration" as DiscordBotConfiguration
object "Discord bot credential" as DiscordBotCredential <<database>>
Sysadmin --> AdminAPI : 1: submit admin command
AdminAPI --> TeacherUpdate : 2: execute teacher update
TeacherUpdate --> TeacherStorage : 3: load teacher
TeacherStorage --> Teachers : 4: SELECT
TeacherUpdate --> PasswordHasher : 5: hash password when needed
TeacherUpdate --> TeacherStorage : 6: save teacher
TeacherStorage --> Teachers : 7: UPDATE
TeacherUpdate --> AdminAPI : 8: Teacher
AdminAPI --> DiscordBotConfiguration : 9: update bot credential
DiscordBotConfiguration --> DiscordBotCredential : 10: INSERT/UPDATE
AdminAPI --> Sysadmin : 11: response
@enduml
